data.description: Discover luxury living in the prestigious Villages of Savannah, Brandywine, MD in this 5,300+ square foot residence offering the perfect blend of sophistication and comfort, featuring impressive 9' ceilings and an abundance of exquisite features throughout. Step into the grand foyer, adorned with hardwood flooring and into the formal living room and dining room areas.  Main-level second primary bedroom with a full bath, walk-in closet, tray ceilings, and a dedicated HVAC system—a perfect guest suite or in-law arrangement. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with stainless steel appliances, a large island, a gas stove, double oven, an inviting eat-in area, a walk-in pantry, and a newer garbage disposal. Cozy up by the gas fireplace in the adjacent spacious family room area. A large office space with built-ins. Nice sized laundry room. Lovely screened-in porch, added just four years ago. Paver back porch secluded by trees. A shed on the property provides additional storage. Brand new roof! Ascend the stairs to find four generously-sized bedrooms, each featuring large walk-in closets. The primary bedroom includes an expansive sitting area, large walk-in closet and en suite bath with oversized shower and a gorgeous soaking tub.The finished basement  features a dedicated theatre room, a huge bonus room that can be used as an additional bedroom, gym, or versatile flex space. Rest easy with a whole-house generator, ensuring you're never left in the dark. This property offers a perfect commuter location with nearby routes leading to Washington, D.C., and Virginia. **ONE YEAR HOME WARRANTY INCLUDED***$3,000 SELLER CLOSING HELP***
